				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \lambda = \frac{2D\Updelta p}{{L\rho u^{2} }}, $$\end{document}where u is the mean velocity in the tube.Fig. 3
Comparison between simulation and experimental results of friction factor; Sim represents the simulated results in this work, Exp represents the experimental results in Meng (2003)
